cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper involves computer vision (CV) techniques for processing range images captured by a Time-of-Flight (ToF) camera in a robotic arm setup. Therefore, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves robotics (RO) and machine learning (LG) techniques, which are closely related to the topic. Additionally, the paper proposes a learning-based approach using deep learning (AI) and conducts experimental validations (GR).
